heading: Penitent Cairns Dungeon Guide
content: Penitent Cairns fast dungeon but with low value monster families and and the nearly worthless . It's a quick one for the Renown though, so put this one on your Renown farming speedrun route potentially. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
